ing: 1 (9 inch) deep dish pie crust, baked and cooled
1 (1.4 ounce) package instant sugar-free chocolate pudding mix
1/2 cup frozen reduced-calorie whipped topping, thawed
des: "A great sugarless pie!  Other flavors of sugar free pudding are great too!"
ins: Prepare pudding as directed on package for pie. Spoon into pie shell, and chill 1 hour. Serve with whipped topping.
